    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and shows clear signs of its age and regular use. The exterior has several visible scratches, minor door dings, and some fading on the clear coat in certain areas. Inside, the upholstery shows noticeable wear and staining, though it remains intact. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it may require some upcoming maintenance to address minor leaks and suspension wear. This is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional daily driver who doesn't mind some cosmetic imperfections and minor mechanical needs.",
