    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Ready for a reliable new companion? This fantastic vehicle is in great shape and has been well-maintained, offering a smooth and dependable driving experience. While it shows some light, expected signs of previous use, it remains a clean and attractive choice for anyone looking for quality and value. You'll love the way it handles on the road!",
