    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior is clean with only minor surface scratches and small door dings consistent with regular use, while the interior remains tidy with no major tears or stains. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a consistent service history, making it a dependable choice for anyone looking for a quality pre-owned car that is ready for the road.",
