      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s looking for a new home! This car has been super reliable for me and is still in really solid shape. It\u2019s been well-loved and taken care of, so it runs like a dream and is ready to hit the road with you today. Perfect for someone who wants a dependable vehicle without the brand-new price tag. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself\u2014you're going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine, paired with a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. This chassis has been maintained with mechanical longevity in mind; the VANOS system has been overhauled and rod bearings have been addressed to ensure the 8,000 RPM redline remains reliable. Power is delivered through a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential, providing exceptional lateral grip and exit speed. The rear subframe\u2014a known point of fatigue\u2014has been reinforced for structural rigidity. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the individual throttle bodies (ITBs) are perfectly synced, and the suspension kinematics remain sharp. This is a mechanically sound, enthusiast-spec example ready for the apex.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Clean title. Maintenance records available. Reliable engine. Minor cosmetic wear.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and care, presenting in impressive condition for its age. The exterior retains a high-gloss finish, with only minor cosmetic blemishes consistent with responsible daily use. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean; the seats show minimal bolster wear, the carpets are free of stains, and the dashboard remains crack-free. All technological components, including the navigation system and premium audio, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is sound, having followed a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the suspension remains tight and responsive. Recent service includes a fresh oil change and a comprehensive multi-point inspection, ensuring this car is road-ready. It comes with a complete set of floor mats, two keys, and a detailed service history log.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
